STATE
v.
Napoleon Junior RANKIN. No. 40P15-4. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 5, 2015. Catherine F. Jordan, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Napoleon J. Rankin, Lumberton, for Rankins, Napoleon Junior. J. Douglas Henderson, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of September 2015 by Defendant for Production and Disclosure:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of November 2015."
